#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.128"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.128:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.128:0.2"
msgid "13. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "13. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.128:0.3"
msgid "128. Tatiyasamudayadhammasutta"
msgstr "128. Liable To Originate (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.173"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.128:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca mahākoṭṭhiko bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye … pe …"
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta and Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita were staying near Benares, in the deer park at Isipatana. …"

msgctxt "sn22.128:1.2"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Mahākoṭṭhita said to Sāriputta:"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn22.128:1.3"
msgid "“‘vijjā, vijjā’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘knowledge’."

msgctxt "sn22.128:1.4"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, vijjā;"
msgstr "What is knowledge?"

msgctxt "sn22.128:1.5"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr "And how is a knowledgeable person defined?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.128:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, sutavā ariyasāvako samudayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; vayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ … pe … samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ rūpan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti;"
msgstr "“Reverend, it’s when an educated noble disciple truly understands form, which is liable to originate … liable to vanish … liable to originate and vanish, as form which is liable to originate and vanish."

msgctxt "sn22.128:2.2"
msgid "samudayadhammaṃ vedanaṃ … pe … samudayavayadhammā vedanā …"
msgstr "They truly understand feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.128:2.3"
msgid "samudayadhammaṃ saññaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.128:2.4"
msgid "samudayadhamme saṅkhāre … vayadhamme saṅkhāre … samudayavayadhamme saṅkhāre ‘samudayavayadhammā saṅkhārā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.128:2.5"
msgid "Samudayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ … vayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ … samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘samudayavayadhammaṃ viññāṇan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "consciousness, which is liable to originate … liable to vanish … liable to originate and vanish, as consciousness which is liable to originate and vanish."

msgctxt "sn22.128:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, vijjā;"
msgstr "This is called knowledge."

msgctxt "sn22.128:2.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti."
msgstr "And this is how a knowledgeable person is defined.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.128:2.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
